lead_paragraph: The former president of the company owned by Cleveland Browns owner Jimmy Haslam and Tennessee Gov. Bill Haslam will face trial next year along with seven others on charges they conspired to cheat customers out of promised discounts and rebates.

headline.main: Former Executives of Haslam-Owned Chain Get 2017 Trial Date
headline.print_headline: Former Executives of Haslam-Owned Chain Get 2017 Trial Date
